<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>59</hymn_number>
<title>JOY TO THE WORLD</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Vannuoi kipak hen, Lalpa hung!
 Leiin a Leng lawp hen;
 Lunggil chengin mun bawlsak hen;
 Van leh lei in sau hen(2)
 Van leh.....leiin zaila sau hen.

[V2]
 2. Vannuoi kipak hen, vai A hawm,
 Singchan zailan awi hen;
 Gam leh lui suongpi, muol leh phai;
 Kipah la sa nawn un (2)
 Kipah.....kipah la sa nawn un.

[V3]
 3. Thutak, lungsietnan vai a hawm,
 Namtin A hetchet sak;
 A dikna, A lopizie chu,
 Leh A lungsiet mak zie (2)
 Leh A....leh A lungsiet mak zie.</lyrics>
</song>